column2: select   i.ra,i.dec,i.Z,i.Z_WARNING,l.OIII_#_FLUX,l.OIII_#_FLUX_ERR,l.NII_#_FLUX,l.NII_#_FLUX_ERR,l.H_ALPHA_FLUX,l.H_ALPHA_FLUX_ERR,l.H_BETA_FLUX,l.H_BETA_FLUX_ERR,l.specObjID into for_BPT    from galSpecline as l join SpecObjALL as s    on l.specObjID=s.specObjID join galSpecinfo as i   on l.specObjID=i.specObjID    where s.scienceprimary=#
